caption:
🗓️ GradSWE is kicking off the year with 8 online info sessions from Wednesday, Sept 18 to Friday, Sept 27! We are excited to introduce you to GradSWE and tell you about all the events and opportunities within our club. Sign up using the QR code! 

All registrants who attend the session will be entered in a raffle to win one of two $20 UofT Bookstore gift cards 📚
